Name: Cubic Dweller
About the game: Cubic Dweller is a tricky platformer with hard jumps and crazy boss fights. You will see a death counter on the screen to see how many times you died in the game so you can push through and finish each level. This game may be hard but it is really fun. The graphics are kinda retro but look nice. I hope you have fun playing my game! Thanks.
